.wrapper
  .Title
    内訳･詳細表示
  .Regular__form
    .Regular__form__content
      .Regular__form__content__settlement
        .Regular__form__content__settlement__check
          ■決済はコチラからです
          = form_with url: check_breakdowns_path, local: true, method: :get, class: "" do |f|
            = f.label "コミュニケーター"
            = f.collection_select(:user_id, User.where(admin: false), :id, :name, {prompt: true}, {class:"table_style"})
            = f.label "時期"
            = f.date_select :dating, {discard_day:true,use_month_numbers:true, date_separator:'年'}, class: 'table_style'
            = "月"
            = f.submit "内訳書検索", class: "btn btn-lg btn-outline-danger"
        .Regular__form__content__settlement__check
          ■帳票確認はコチラからです(コミュニケーター指定は不要です)
